===============================================================================
Linux SUSI Driver
===============================================================================

        Please carefully read the terms and conditions in license.rtf

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to install/uninstall SUSI driver & run demo AP
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        1) Extract the gzip file.
           user$ tar zxf SUSI5_DEMO_SAMPLE.gz
        2) Execute install.sh to install SUSI.
           root# ./SUSI5.0.X/Driver/install.sh
        3) Execute demo AP.
           root# ./SUSI5.0.X/Susi4Demo/susidemo4
        4) Execute install.sh with parameter "u" to uninstall SUSI.
           root# ./SUSI5.0.X/Driver/install.sh u

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install Nvidia driver for SusiAiDemo & reading the docker container infomation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        1) For example, Ubuntu 18.04, 20.04, 22.04 recommend
           root# apt install nvidia-driver-515 nvidia-dkms-515
           root# apt install nvidia-384
        2) For example, pull and then run Ubuntu Docker image
           root# docker pull ubuntu
           root# docker run -it --rm --privileged ubuntu
        3) Execute SUSI AI demo AP.
           root# ./SUSI5.0.X/SusiAiDemo/SusiAiDemo

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Compile Sample Sources AP
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        1) *.c are the sample sources.
        2) Make sure all libSUSI-4.00.* in your sample sources folder.
        3) Refer to "Makefile", then use "make" to compile it.
